name: North End, 1 Bed Apt w/ office, Boston
neighborhood_overview: Boston's North End is a distinct community central to public transportation, fine dining and bakeries and tourist destinations. Enjoy a short walk to the Seaport, Faneuil Hall and the Financial District. The North End is central to Quincy Market and Faneuil Hall, the Financial District and the Boston Seaport.
description:
